{
  "stem": "2460.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were yelling in Yiddish and Polish and Hungarian, all the different languages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But fast.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Fast.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Fast.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was very, very scary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was probably the scariest moment in my life 'til then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very scary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and they told us to separate, to-- the children here with the mothers and the-- the older people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my father, he was a young man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "43 years old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "39 years old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother grabbed my little brother, Gabi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father grabbed me from the one side, and my older brother from the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, you are coming with me because you're a bar mitzvah boy already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And probably this is the reason I'm here today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING] And we saw that they are taking away the-- the little children, the mothers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING] I didn't have even a chance to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] We just waved them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they're waving back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they told us that the women with the children, they are going to different areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were standing in lines, like soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And passing by, Mengele.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know who was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I saw a tall German and boots with a stick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he just, left, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for some reason, he let me go with my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All my friends in my age-- not all of them, most of them-- went with their mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went with my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were walking through this barbed-wire camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw this strange-looking people coming close to the barbed wires and begging us that we should throw them whatever we have in our pockets.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't have too much because everything left in the boxcar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- but mainly Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
